column4: Hello, how do I make modprobe use my newly compiled /lib/modules/2.6.22-11-generic/kernel/sound/pci/hda/snd-hda-intel.ko instead of the old /lib/modules/2.6.22-11-generic/ubuntu/media/snd-hda-intel/snd-hda-intel.ko?
OMG MY SOUND WORKS AFTER like 11 weeks of on and off attempts!! I am so happy omg omg!
just sudo rm it and sudo depmod
